sub_title: Senior R&D Engineer at PTW Benelux B.V. | Medical Imaging & Radiation Therapy
summary: Biomedical (M.Sc.) and electronic (B.Sc.) engineer with experience on radiotherapy technology (service and quality assurance), telemedicine (research, design, development and support) and medical image analysis/processing. Especially interested in the development and improvement of imaging tools to be used in (radiation) oncology and medical imaging, and in biomedical instrumentation in general.
